<font color=#FFFF00>Ini berat sekali.</font>

329
00:28:25,305 --> 00:28:26,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagus!</font>

330
00:28:30,305 --> 00:28:31,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Pertama dan kedua.</font>

331
00:28:34,035 --> 00:28:35,535
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kelihatan seperti Harimau. (LoL)</font>

332
00:28:37,875 --> 00:28:39,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menginginkan ketegangan.</font>

333
00:28:39,175 --> 00:28:40,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku terus saja mengatakan "malam ini".</font>

334
00:28:43,605 --> 00:28:44,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti itu.</font>

335
00:28:45,575 --> 00:28:46,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Di tengah!</font>

336
00:28:52,375 --> 00:28:53,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Cut.</font>

337
00:28:55,075 --> 00:28:57,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagus. Kerja bagus.</font>

338
00:29:03,435 --> 00:29:05,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Turun, lalu bangun.</font>

339
